rand Final revealed!|url=http://www.eurovision.tv/page/news?id=running_order_for_grand_final_revealed|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|accessdate=22 May 2015}}</ref>\n! Country<ref name=\"ESC 2015 Final\">{{cite web|title=Eurovision Song Contest 2015 Grand final|url=http://www.eurovision.tv/page/history/by-year/contest?event=2083|publisher=Eurovision Song Contest|accessdate=6 March 2015}}</ref>\n! Artist<ref name=\"ESC 2015 Final\"/>\n! Song<ref name=\"ESC 2015 Final\"/>\n! Language\n! Place<ref name=\"ESC 2015 Final\"/>\n! Points\n|-\n| 01\n| {{Esc|Slovenia|y=2015}}\n| [[Maraaya]]\n| \"[[Here for You (Maraaya song)|Here for You]]\"\n| English\n| 14\n| 39\n|-\n| 02\n| {{Esc|France|y=2015}}\n| [[Lisa Angell]]\n| \"[[N'oubliez pas]]\"\n| French\n| 25\n| 4\n|-\n| 03\n| {{Esc|Israel|y=2015}}\n| [[Nadav Guedj]]\n| \"[[Golden Boy (Nadav Guedj song)|Golden Boy]]\"\n| English\n| 9\n| 97\n|-\n| 04\n| {{Esc|Estonia|y=2015}}\n| [[Elina Born]] & [[Stig R\u00e4sta]]\n| \"[[Goodbye to Yesterday (Elina Born & Stig R\u00e4sta song)|Goodbye to Yesterday]]\"\n| English\n| 7\n| 106\n|-\n| 05\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom|y=2015}}\n| [[Electro Velvet]]\n| \"[[Still in Love with You (Electro Velvet song)|Still in Love with You]]\"\n| English\n| 24\n| 5\n|-\n| 06\n| {{Esc|Armenia|y=2015}}\n| [[Genealogy (band)|Genealogy]]\n| \"[[Face the Shadow]]\"\n| English\n| 16\n| 34\n|-\n| 07\n| {{Esc|Lithuania|y=2015}}\n| [[Monika Linkyt\u0117]] & [[Vaidas Baumila]]\n| \"[[This Time (Monika Linkyt\u0117 & Vaidas Baumila song)|This Time]]\"\n| English\n| 18\n| 30\n|-\n| 08\n| {{Esc|Serbia|y=2015}}\n| [[Bojana Stamenov]]\n| \"[[Beauty Never Lies]]\"\n| English\n| 10\n| 53\n|-\n| 09\n| {{Esc|Norway|y=2015}}\n| [[Kjetil M\u00f8rland|M\u00f8rland]] & [[Debrah Scarlett]]\n| \"[[A Monster Like Me]]\"\n| English\n| 8\n| 102\n|- style=\"font-weight: bold; background: gold;\"\n| 10\n| {{Esc|Sweden|y=2015}}\n| [[M\u00e5ns Zelmerl\u00f6w]]\n| \"[[Heroes (M\u00e5ns Zelmerl\u00f6w song)|Heroes]]\"\n| English\n| 1