ntz and Johan Lindroos ([[Yle TV2]] and [[Yle Radio Vega]], all shows)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://yle.fi/aihe/artikkeli/2015/04/07/pertti-kurikan-nimipaivien-h-hetki-lahestyy-tutustu-ylen-laajaan|title=Pertti Kurikan nimip\u00e4ivien h-hetki l\u00e4hestyy \u2013 tutustu Ylen laajaan euroviisuohjelmistoon|date=7 April 2015|language=Finnish|trans-title=Zero hours of Pertti Kurikan nimip\u00e4iv\u00e4t is approaching \u2013 check out the wide Eurovision programming of Yle|accessdate=9 April 2015}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|France}} France&nbsp;\u2013 [[Mareva Galanter]] and J\u00e9r\u00e9my Parayre ([[France \u00d4]], first semi-final);<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.programme-television.org/news-tv/Mareva-Galater-et-Jeremy-Parayre-duo-inedit-pour-la-demie-finale-de-l-Eurovision-France-O-4140323|title=Eurovision 2015 (France \u00d4) : l'autre duo de pr\u00e9sentateurs|language=French|trans-title=Eurovision 2015 (France \u00d4): the other duo presenters|date=27 February 2015|accessdate=6 March 2015|publisher=programme-television.org}}</ref> [[St\u00e9phane Bern]] and Marianne James ([[France 2]], final)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvmag.lefigaro.fr/programme-tv/article/television/85423/eurovision-marianne-james-et-stephane-bern-a-la-presentation.html|title=Eurovision: Marianne James et St\u00e9phane Bern \u00e0 la pr\u00e9sentation|language=French|trans-title=Eurovision: Marianne James and St\u00e9phane Bern presenters.|accessdate=22 February 2015}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Georgia}} Georgia&nbsp;\u2013 Lado Tatishvili and Tamuna Museridze ([[First Channel (Georgian TV channel)|GPB First Channel]], all shows)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eurovision-georgia.ge/news-view/1290/en |title=First Channel of GPB will air the 2015 ESC Live |date=9 May 2015 |accessdate=12 May 2015 |publisher=[[Georgian Public Broadcaster|GPB]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518100551/http://eurovision-georgia.ge/news-view/1290/en |archivedate=18 May 2015  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=