07/comunicat-de-presa-eurovision-2015-12-40-45|work=[[AGERPRES]]|accessdate=10 May 2015|date=7 May 2015|language=Romanian|trans-title=Press release \u2013 Eurovision 2015}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Russia}} Russia&nbsp;\u2013 [[Yana Churikova]] and Yuriy Aksyuta ([[Channel One Russia]], all shows)<ref>{{cite news|first1=Daria|last1=Turtseva|first2=Rinat|last2=Nazmetdinov|url=http://sntat.ru/reportages/7210-yana_churikova_evrovidenie_-_eto_geopoliticheskiy_konkurs_a_ne_muzykalnyy|title=\u042f\u043d\u0430 \u0427\u0443\u0440\u0438\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0430: \u0415\u0432\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u2013 \u044d\u0442\u043e \u0433\u0435\u043e\u043f\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0442\u0438\u0447\u0435\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u043a\u0443\u0440\u0441, \u0430 \u043d\u0435 \u043c\u0443\u0437\u044b\u043a\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439|trans-title=Yana Churikova \u2013 Eurovision is a geopolitical contest, not a musical|date=10 April 2015|publisher=\u0421\u043e\u0431\u044b\u0442\u0438\u044f|language=Russian|accessdate=14 April 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415041523/http://sntat.ru/reportages/7210-yana_churikova_evrovidenie_-_eto_geopoliticheskiy_konkurs_a_ne_muzykalnyy|archive-date=15 April 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|San Marino}} San Marino&nbsp;\u2013 Lia Fiorio and Gigi Restivo ([[SMtv San Marino (TV channel)|SMtv San Marino]] and [[SMtv San Marino|Radio San Marino]], all shows)<ref>{{cite news|url=http://eurofestivalnews.com/2015/04/13/san-marino-rtv-al-commento-ancora-lia-fiorio-e-gigi-restivo/|title=San Marino RTV, al commento ancora Lia Fiorio e Gigi Restivo|trans-title=San Marino RTV, the comment still Lia Fiorio and Gigi Restivo|date=13 April 2015|publisher=Eurofestival News|language=Italian|accessdate=13 April 2015}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Serbia}} Serbia&nbsp;\u2013 [[Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107-Lu\u010di\u0107|Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107]] ([[RTS 1]], [[Radio Television of Serbia|RTS HD]] and [[Radio Television of Serbia|RTS SAT]], first semi-final and final); Silvana Gruji\u0107 ([[RTS 2]] and [[Radio Television of Serbia|RTS SAT]], second semi-final)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/ci/story/17/%D0%A0%D0%A2%D0%A1+1/1920608/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BC%D0%B0+%D0%95%D0%B2%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5+2015%3A+%D0%9F%D1%80%D0%B2%D0%BE+%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%83%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B5%2C+%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81.html|title=\u041f\u0435\u0441\u043c\u0430 \u0415\u0432\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0437\u0438\u0458\u0435 2015: \u041f\u0440\u0432\u043e \u043f\u043e\u043b\u0443\u0444\u0438\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0435, \u043f\u0440\u0435\u043d\u043e\u0441|trans-title=Eurovision 2015: First semi-final transfer|date=15 May 2015|accessdate=15 May 2015|publisher=[[Radio Television of Serbia]]|language=Serbian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/ci/story/18/%D0%A0%D0%A2%D0%A1+2/1925196/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BC%D0%B0+%D0%95%D0%B2%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5+2015%3A+%D0%94%D1%80%D1%83%D0%B3%D0%BE+%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%83%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B5%2C+%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81.html|title=\u041f\u0435\u0441\u043c\u0430 \u0415\u0432\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0437\u0438\u0458\u0435 2015: \u0414\u0440\u0443\u0433\u043e \u043f\u043e\u043b\u0443\u0444\u0438\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0435, \u043f\u0440\u0435\u043d\u043e\u0441|trans-title=Eurovision 2015: Second semi-final transfer|date=20 May 2015|accessdate=20 May 2015|publisher=[[Radio Television of Serbia]]|language=Serbian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/ci/story/17/%D0%A0%D0%A2%D0%A1+1/1927428/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BC%D0%B0+%D0%95%D0%B2%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5+2015%3A+%D0%A4%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B5%2C+%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81.html|title=\u041f\u0435\u0441\u043c\u0430 \u0415\u0432\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0437\u0438\u0458\u0435 2015: \u0424\u0438\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0435, \u043f\u