zhagam|DMK]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{DMK/meta/color}}\" rowspan=1|\n|| [[H. D. Dewe Gowda]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Sikandar Bakht]]\n|\n| 19 March 1998\n| 13 October 1999\n|| [[Bharatiya Janata Party]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{Bharatiya Janata Party/meta/color}}\" rowspan=1|\n|| [[Atal Bihari Vajpayee]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n|}\n\n===Past Ministers: Commerce===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Portrait\n! colspan=2|Term of office\n! colspan=2|Party\n! Prime Minister\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[I. I. Chundrigar]]\n| [[File:No image.svg|60px]]\n| 2 September 1946\n| 14 August 1947\n|| [[All-India Muslim League]]\n|  style=\"width:4px; background:green;\"|\n|| [[Jawaharlal Nehru]]<br><small>(as Vice President of the Executive Council)\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Cooverji Hormusji Bhabha]] <br>''(Commerce)''\n| \n| 15 August 1947\n| 06 April 1948\n|rowspan=14| [[Indian National Congress]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{Indian National Congress/meta/color}}\" rowspan=14|\n|rowspan=9| [[Jawaharlal Nehru]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Kshitish Chandra Neogy]] <br>''(Commerce)''\n| \n| 06 April 1948\n| 19 April 1950\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Jawaharlal Nehru]]<br>''(Commerce and Industry)''\n|\n| 19 April 1950\n| 13 May 1950\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Sri Prakasa]] <br>''(Commerce)''\n| \n| 29 May 1950\n| 26 December 1950\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Harekrushna Mahtab]] <br>''(Commerce and Industry)''\n| \n| 26 December 1950 \n| 13 May 1952\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[T T Krishnamachari]] <br>''(Commerce and Industry)''\n| \n| 13 May 1952 \n| 30 August 1956\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Morarji Desai]] <br>''(Commerce and Industry)''\n| \n| 1 January 1957 \n| 28 March 1958\n|-\n| [[Lal Bahadur Shastri]]<br>''(Commerce and Industry)''   \n| \n| 28 March 1958\n| 05 April 1961\n|-\n| [[KC Reddy]] <br>''(Commerce and Industry)''\n| \n| 05 April 1961\n| 19 July 1963 \n|-\n| [[Manubhai 