ngh (politician)|Ajit Singh]]<ref name=iandc /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://164.100.47.132/LssNew/members/former_Biography.aspx?mpsno=14 |title=Fifteenth Lok Sabha, Members Bioprofile :Singh,Shri Ajit |website=loksabha.nic.in |publisher=[[National Informatics Centre]] |accessdate=August 29, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304022948/http://164.100.47.132/LssNew/members/former_Biography.aspx?mpsno=14 |archive-date=4 March 2016 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n| \n| 5 December 1989\n| 10 November 1990\n|| [[Janata Dal]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{Janata Dal/meta/color}}\" rowspan=1|\n|| [[V. P. Singh]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[K. Karunakaran]]\n|\n| 11 June 1995\n| 16 May 1996\n|| [[Indian National Congress]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{Indian National Congress/meta/color}}\" rowspan=1|\n|| [[P. V. Narasimha Rao]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Suresh Prabhu]]\n|\n| 16 May 1996\n| 1 June 1996\n|| [[Bharatiya Janata Party]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{Bharatiya Janata Party/meta/color}}\" rowspan=1|\n|| [[Atal Bihari Vajpayee]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Murasoli Maran]]\n|\n| 1 June 1996\n| 19 March 1998\n|| [[Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam|DMK]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{DMK/meta/color}}\" rowspan=1|\n|| [[H. D. Dewe Gowda]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[Sikandar Bakht]]\n|\n| 19 March 1998\n| 13 October 1999\n|| [[Bharatiya Janata Party]]\n|width=\"4px\" bgcolor=\"{{Bharatiya Janata Party/meta/color}}\" rowspan=1|\n|| [[Atal Bihari Vajpayee]]\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n|}\n\n===Past Ministers: Commerce===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Portrait\n! colspan=2|Term of office\n! colspan=2|Party\n! Prime Minister\n|- style=\"height: 50px;\"\n| [[I. I. Chundrigar]]\n| [[File:No image.svg|60px]]\n| 2 September 1946\n| 14 August 1947\n|| [[All-India Muslim League]]\n|  style=\"width:4px; background:green;\"|\n|| [[Jawaharlal Nehru]]<br><small>(as Vice President of the Executive Council)\n|- style=